description: Enjoy elevated living at this prized corner of Echelon Seaport, this 2 bed, 2.5 bath residence offers dramatic harbor, city, and sunset views through walls of glass. Among the most sought-after floor plans in the building, it features two expansive ensuite bedrooms, a refined powder room, and an airy living/dining space ideal for entertaining. The sleek kitchen is outfitted with Thermador integrated appliances, 5 burner gas cooktop,  and exceptional storage. Two valet spaces included. Echelon Seaport pampers residents with 24/7 concierge, doorman, and resort-style amenities including indoor and outdoor pools, basketball court, golf simulator, spa, wine room, and curated dining and retail at your doorstep. Experience vibrant Seaport living at its finest, where an abundance of outdoor terraces and world-class amenities redefine everyday luxury.
